#

Lemon Herb Grilled Salmon

25 min
$12
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main DishDinner

Tags:

HealthyQuickGrilled

Description

A light and zesty salmon dish that's perfect for a quick and healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz each)
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • fresh parsley (chopped): 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
